model.name: Shoulder Tab Shirt
model.disambiguatingDescription: A timeless style with a twist. This shirt is cut from lightweight, breathable Oxford cotton poplin in a comfortable masculine fit. Simple shoulder tabs introduce an understated uniform detail, while the classic shade is offset with contrasting buttons and subtle LV Circle signatures on the front pocket and embossed leather patch on the hem.

additionalProperty.name: detailedDescription
additionalProperty.value:
• Main Material : 100% Cotton
  • Other Material : 100% Calfskin
  • Bleu Oxford, Blue
  • Regular fit
  • Model wears size 36
  • Model measurements : Bust 32'' / 81 cm, Height 5' 9" / 174 cm, Waist 23'' / 58 cm, Hips 34'' / 86 cm
  • Made in Italy
  • Do not wash
  • Do not bleach
  • Do not tumble dry
  • Iron at a maximum sole-plate temperature of 110°C
  • Mild professionnal dry cleaning in hydrocarbons
